@using BForms.Docs.Helpers
<h3 id="Input-NumberPicker">Number Picker Input</h3>

<p>        
    In order to render a text input of type number picker you will need to use the 
    <code>@@Html.BsInputFor</code> helper extension and 
    decorate your model property with <code>[BsControl(BsControlType.Number)]</code>. Also the model property must be of type <code>BsRangeItem&lt;int&gt;</code>.
</p>

